"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.5.2.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.5.2.1</span> 标题：雕刻（engraving, carving）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חרשׁ, חָרָשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：charash)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:11\">EXO 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:35\">EXO 35:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:23\">EXO 38:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1\">JER 17:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חֲרֹשֶׁת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：charosheth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:5\">EXO 31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:5\">EXO 31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:33\">EXO 35:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:33\">EXO 35:33</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：פתח</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：pathach（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:9\">EXO 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:11\">EXO 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36\">EXO 28:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:6\">EXO 39:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:6\">2CH 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13\">2CH 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:9\">ZEC 3:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：פִּתּוּחַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：pituach)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:11\">EXO 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:21\">EXO 28:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36\">EXO 28:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:6\">EXO 39:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:14\">EXO 39:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:30\">EXO 39:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:6\">2CH 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13\">2CH 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:6\">PSA 74:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:9\">ZEC 3:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：קלע, מִקְלַעַת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：qala‘（动词）, miqla‘ath)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:18\">1KI 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29\">1KI 6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29\">1KI 6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:32\">1KI 6:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:32\">1KI 6:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:31\">1KI 7:31</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：γλύμμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：glumma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:27\">SIR 38:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir45:11\">SIR 45:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：γλυφή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：glufē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis18:24\">WIS 18:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：γλύφω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：glufō（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis13:13\">WIS 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:27\">SIR 38:27</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἐγγλύφω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：egglufō（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:29\">1MA 13:29</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κολάπτω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kolaptō（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir45:11\">SIR 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc2:27\">3MA 2:27</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0341_engraving_ring.jpg\" alt=\"戒指上的雕刻\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">戒指上的雕刻 (© The Portable Antiquities Scheme/ The Trustees of the British Museum, CC BY-SA 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>雕刻作品是通过在石头、金属或宝石等坚硬表面上刻画线条来完成创作的图画或文字。木雕通常是用木头制成的像，用刀或其他锋利的工具削刻而成。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在有些语言中，可能需要根据雕刻表面的材质来选择合适的“雕刻”动词。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:5\">EXO 31:5</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:33\">EXO 35:33</a> 中，希伯来文<em>charosheth</em> 指雕刻作品和木雕。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:27\">SIR 38:27</a> 中描述的具体动作是“刻印”（“engrave seals”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> ；比较更加准确的<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 译法，“cut the signets of seals”“雕刻印章上的印记”；另参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">10.2 印、印章、印戒、打印的戒指、戒指 (seal, signet ring, ring)&lt;REALIA:10.2&gt;</a> 中的讨论）。这段经文的重点是雕刻师的勤奋和精确。如果当地没有准确对应“印”的词语，可以参考其他需要精确做工、样式繁多的手工艺品，以找到合适的译词。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
